Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Faculty, Student
    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the User Class. It incorporates each user's essential identity details, being the abstract parent class. Details include their first name, last name, id, email, and password
    Author:
    Sarah Heckman
